This repository contains the files and script to get positively-selected sites being significantly favored in repeat reions in genes in a clade-wise manner.

We have already kept the result files in the directory, but if you wish to generate them, you can do so by running the following command:
bash bedtools_fisher_script.sh

"bedtools_fisher_script.sh" is the name of the shell script (run it on terminal; it may not work on Windows system).
We have added some instructions inside the script for the readers to understand it.
To read the script type:
cat bedtools_fisher_script.sh

Note: Please make sure you are in the same directory on your terminal which contains the files.
